TITLE: Configuring Tauri App in Rust
DESCRIPTION: This function sets up and runs a Tauri application. It includes configuration for the HTTP plugin and opens developer tools for the main window.
SOURCE: https://github.com/leptos-rs/leptos/blob/main/projects/tauri-from-scratch/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_13

